Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Head MRI
When I select 'Cognitive changes' from 'Previous interventions/therapies' dropdown menu
Then 'Add clinic' button is enabled
And 'Impaired concentration' radio button is enabled
And 'Loss of short-term memory' radio button is enabled
And 'Loss of long-term memory' radio button is enabled
And 'Memory impairment' radio button is enabled
